ROYAL UNION MUT. LIFE INS. CO. v. WYNN et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. March 28, 1911.) No. 2,094. Appeal from Circuit Court of the United States for the Northern District of Georgia. Henry R. Goetehius, for appellant. William A. Wimbish and Edgar Watkins, for appellees.

Before PARDEE and SHELBY, Circuit Judges, and TOULMIN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

As we find no reversible error in this record, the judgment of the Circuit Court (177 Fed. 289) is affirmed.
